{"tid":1032391,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 換電","createTime":"2019-02-22T10:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T16:59:55.000Z","uid":238473,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad69622c9047a869c4d40de5db439348c58f38c","tid":1032391,"uid":238473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"電跌得太快，返工無時間去apple換，去左先達搵間即場5分鐘換好，諗住無死啦，可以頂返半年。<br />\n<br />\n吊，但幾日後朝早，開唔到機，叉電又唔著。羅返去問先達個野，話我部機漏電，佢用非正常方法叉返著部機。<br />\n<br />\n佢話部機要維持有30%電，唔係就有機會開唔返我吊，部機俾佢整完仲衰左。<br />\n<br />\n好撚大機會佢整撚壞，我想嘈佢叫佢攪返好，有無得諗？"},{"pid":"8b9cdfed1378f8db328bafb20c394671ddcfd44a","tid":1032391,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"佢識整就唔會變成咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32eead88be257e45122a4d3a4156db92ff4a80f","tid":1032391,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"effdee81e9915405852a49a7700f317cfc4fc9b6","tid":1032391,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"過保未？咩形號？"},{"pid":"55b9ff2a4dddf3f9cc5e30b745b05833eafdc209","tid":1032391,"uid":19609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"cls pg<br />\n慳幾百輸幾千係唔係呢d?"},{"pid":"f4cbb8c79857370846c110aa9fbc1e015fbac599","tid":1032391,"uid":19183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b9cdfed1378f8db328bafb20c394671ddcfd44a","tid":1032391,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"佢識整就唔會變成咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99895f22c75e9433f715a04e2f68efbc3e4ff230","tid":1032391,"uid":220721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被